<div class="container">

  <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="height: 100px;">
    <h1>ゾンビさがし</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center" style="height: 100px;">
    <p>ここはいろいろなゾンビを取り扱っています<br>
    まずは診断からあなた好みのゾンビを探してみましょう</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
    <div class="col-md-4 justify-content-center align-items-center">
      <%= link_to "診断してみる", diagnose_path , class: "btn btn-info btn-block", style:"height: 200px;"%>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-1">
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4 bg-info rounded d-flex justify-content-center" style="height: 200px;">
      <div class="d-flex flex-column">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center text-light m-4">
          <span>カテゴリから探す</span>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center">
          <%= link_to "すべて", zombies_path, class: "btn btn-light btn-sm m-1" %>
            <%= link_to "映画", zombies_path(tag_name: "映画"), class: "btn btn-light btn-sm m-1" %>
            <%= link_to "ドラマ", zombies_path(tag_name: "ドラマ"), class: "btn btn-light btn-sm m-1" %>
            <%= link_to "アニメ", zombies_path(tag_name: "アニメ"), class: "btn btn-light btn-sm m-1" %>
            <%= link_to "ゲーム", zombies_path(tag_name: "ゲーム"), class: "btn btn-light btn-sm m-1" %>
            <%= link_to "アプリ", zombies_path(tag_name: "スマホアプリ"), class: "btn btn-light btn-sm m-1" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <% if logged_in? %>
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mt-5">
      <%= link_to"ログアウト", logout_path, method: :delete,class:"btn btn-outline-info btn-sm" %>
    </div>
  <% else %>
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mt-5">
      <p>ユーザー登録をすると、ゾンビ情報の投稿・レビュー投稿・<br>お気に入り機能が使えるようになります！</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center m-2">
      <%= link_to"新規登録", signup_path,class:"btn btn-outline-info btn-sm"%>
    </div>

    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
      <%= link_to"ログイン", login_path,class:"btn btn-outline-info btn-sm" %>
    </div>
  <% end %>





</div>